    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《懒人塔防》是一款爽快解压的放置类塔防割草游戏。如果你厌倦了需要时时刻刻的操作，讨厌总是随机不到自己想要的道具。那么这是一款为你量身打造的懒人爽游。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054090/extras/a5ece6960a041dca48ad9f48c3fd0869.poster.avif?t=1763523673\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054090/extras/a5ece6960a041dca48ad9f48c3fd0869.webm?t=1763523673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054090/extras/a5ece6960a041dca48ad9f48c3fd0869.mp4?t=1763523673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >构筑</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>从一座简单的防御塔开始，搭配模块，设计你的专属构筑。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054090/extras/08de38f20bf1028dd3997f844d99a22c.poster.avif?t=1763523673\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054090/extras/08de38f20bf1028dd3997f844d99a22c.webm?t=1763523673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054090/extras/08de38f20bf1028dd3997f844d99a22c.mp4?t=1763523673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >数十种模块可供选择</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>波次推进获得点数，使用点数解锁模块。简单直接，没有随机。喜欢哪个解锁哪个！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054090/extras/edefaee1ab0fc964b3bfa44d68d01e10.poster.avif?t=1763523673\" width=378 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054090/extras/edefaee1ab0fc964b3bfa44d68d01e10.webm?t=1763523673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054090/extras/edefaee1ab0fc964b3bfa44d68d01e10.mp4?t=1763523673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >放置</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>自动杀敌，获取金币。使用金币升级模块。普通的武器通过简单的升级也将迎来质变。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054090/extras/5515de3d54c4cb42fa356e0b1885ffa2.poster.avif?t=1763523673\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054090/extras/5515de3d54c4cb42fa356e0b1885ffa2.webm?t=1763523673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054090/extras/5515de3d54c4cb42fa356e0b1885ffa2.mp4?t=1763523673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >选择能力，重新开始</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>选择进化，获得强大的能力，以专属形态重新开始。更强的构筑，更快的杀敌，更爽快的体验！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054090/extras/15bab78df8b98a590ee1ec7d465a4a34.poster.avif?t=1763523673\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054090/extras/15bab78df8b98a590ee1ec7d465a4a34.webm?t=1763523673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054090/extras/15bab78df8b98a590ee1ec7d465a4a34.mp4?t=1763523673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
